{{RN}} {{Construction}} {{Joke Game}}{{Game-infobox |expand = Five Nights At Nintendo: With Reggie |image = [[File:FIVENIGHTSNINTENDO3.png|428px]] |descr = The spoopy title screen. |developer = NinRMAX |publisher = Nintendo |platforms = Nintendo 3DS |genre = Point and Click Horror Game}}
'''Five Nights At Nintendo '''is a horror game for the [[Nintendo 3DS]], It features characters like Iwata, Reggie, and Waluigi. The game won the award for "most spoopy game 1889". It was shown at E2 1684.
This is the first Nintendo video game to sell 10 copies, That's amazing.
==Plot== At 12:00am, Nintendo INC's lights goes out, and Reggie yells out the window, he saids "My body is spoopy". Iwata heard the sound and becomes a robot from Please Understand Gen 4. The two both make the company a love hotel like the good ol' days. Later at 8:00am, They open the doors to their building and invite the player in. Locking them up for five nights. The player must surive for the night and dodge knifes, and Sony and Microsoft lovers. If the player dies, they become part of the evil Nintendo team, If the player is safe, They win 17,369 copies of Super Smash Bros. Wii U. ==Characters== {| border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" class="article-table" style="width: 500px;" |- ! scope="col"|[[File:Fivenightsatreggie.png|350px]]Spoopy Reggie is the main character of teh game, He has tons of HP and OP. ! scope="col"| |- |[[File:ReggieMii.png|right]]'''Toy Reggie with spoopy blue pants. He can eat hot pockets when he needs to.''' | |- |TBA | |- |TBA | |}
