== Meaning ==
*title &ndash; default pagename, just in case can be changed
*descr &ndash; description for the image
*species &ndash; the species of a character, i.e, [[Mario]] is a human.
*relations &ndash; relatives, like [[Luigi]] is related to [[Mario]] (they're both brothers)
*gender &ndash; i.e. [[Mona]] is female.
*status &ndash; this states if a character is deceased, ill or any other status (may also be positive). If a character has no special status, Alive is put in.
*nationality &ndash; this states that the nationality of 1 character with it's flag's image.
*affiliation &ndash; i.e., Koopa Troop, X-Naut
*first_appearance &ndash; this states the character's debut.
*latest_appearance &ndash; this states the character's most recent appearance in a game.
*vulnerable &ndash; this states the character's weakness.
*element &ndash; this states the character's main element.
*weapon &ndash; this shows the weapon(s) that the character possesses.
*town &ndash; this shows where the character lives.
*class &ndash; this shows which class or occupation the character has.
*abilities &ndash; this shows the ability/ies the character possesses.
*aliases &ndash; this shows the nickname(s) that the character has
*voice &ndash; this shows who voices the character
*ethnicity &ndash; this shows the ethnicity of the character (only if human usually).
